This was made by me at the end of my first year. It can be directly opened as a netbeans project. You might be required to tune in your netbeans.

Right click the project, go to Properties.
Now under Python subselection, Add the path of your current python installation. In windows it is by default in C:\Python32.

Also remember to use Python version 3.
You may encounter a few error messages when you close the window, simply ignore them for present they do not affect any functionality of the game.